"Specifies how numeric values are formatted in the spreadsheet:"
"<ul><li>Decimal - format as [-]9.9</li><li>Scientific (e) - format as "
"[-]9.9e[+|-]999</li><li>Scientific (E) - format as [-]9.9E[+|-]999</"
